<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="good-n">good <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ɡʊd/    美 /ɡʊd/  </p>
<p>[U]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>好处；用处；利益：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He is optimistic and finds good in all situations.
他很乐观，在各种情况下总能发现事物美好的一面。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>You must try hard <strong>for the good of</strong> the team. 
你必须为全队的利益尽力而为。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>善；善行；合乎道德的行为：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>good and evil
善与恶</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He <strong>did</strong> a lot of <strong>good</strong> for us.
他为我们做了许多好事。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="be-no-good">be no good</h3>
<p>1.<strong>没有用处：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>It is no good watching</strong> so much television.
看这么多电视没什么用。</p></div>

<h3 id="do-good-to">do good (to)</h3>
<p>1.<strong>(对…) 有益：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>People believe that climbing can do good to health.
人们认为登山有益健康。</p><footer>2008 安徽</footer></div>

<h3 id="do-sb-good">do sb good</h3>
<p>1.<strong>对某人有好处：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Thinking that way does you no good.
那样想对你没好处。</p><footer>2013 广东</footer></div>

<h3 id="for-good">for good</h3>
<p>1.<strong>永远：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The murderer will stay in prison for good.
那个谋杀犯将被终身监禁。</p></div></div>